com.ca.mas.identity.common

Interface MASFilteredRequestBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MASFilteredRequest

    public interface MASFilteredRequestBuilder

    MASFilteredRequestBuilder defines all of the SCIM operations that are available for SCIM queries. Each Operator type is represented by a specific method that requires only the attribute(s) and the value in order to create a well-formed representation of the MASRequest serviceable by the SCIM server implementation.

    • Nested Class Summary

      static class  MASFilteredRequestBuilder.Logical

      static class  MASFilteredRequestBuilder.Operator
      Description: The Operator enum are the SCIM binary and unary operators as described in the SCIM Protocol reference section {3.4.4.2 Filtering}.
      static class  MASFilteredRequestBuilder.SortOrder
      Description: The SortOrder enum contains the sorting directives as described in the SCIM Schema reference section {3.4.2.3 Sorting}.
